sert this move in order to keep the f5 -bishop safe.} 13. Rd1 Qc8 14. c4 Ne6 15. Nd2 {Black's pieces lack space and coordination at the moment. White is intending Nf3 - Nh4 . Therefore Black might be forced to surrender the bishop pair.} *

